Heyas all,<br>
<br>
first I'd like to say I ever started this quest, cause there was a rumor the 3rd ring would have amazing stats and overall it would have Flowing Thought 2 or 3 on it.<br>
<br>
So I start killing goblin's in Thurga like a madman and after two weeks around 5 - 8 hours a day of killing these green lil monsters I became an ally to Sarnak.<br>
<br>
I hail Telcha for my first ring (crappy stats) and then turn in the stuff for my 2nd ring (much nicer stats and a 25DS, which is sweet for pvp ;p).<br>
<br>
At that time it was said the 3rd ring or actually a side quest for the 2nd ring was is a shoulder/arms/wrist item. Still no info on a possible 3rd ring. So I start collecting the items for the side quest. Got the Sinew from Trakanon pretty quick (And YES it drops from Juggs as well, we dont need 20 confirms from ppl to state it drops from Juggs ;p) and I got the Urn on the 2nd time I killed Drusella.<br>
<br>
Oh boy what an excitement ! I was finally finishing the side quest, but more important I was hoping for a lead to the real 3rd ring (not the side quest thus P). So I ask my guild rogue to duel me in Chardok and ask her to consent me. I dragged her to the Royals and she opened the door for me.<br>
<br>
Standing in front of her and giving her the items will make her say this:<br>
<br>
Queen Velazul Di`zok says 'Amazing! You have returned the trophies I asked for, against impossible odds.  Here is your reward, worthy minion, may it serve you well. '<br>
<br>
No further lead to a possible 3rd ring 8( Well lets hope for the best, but I doubt it 8(<br>
